[I] XdTV is a software to watch, record and stream TV

[T] XdTV is a software to watch, record and stream TV. It interacts with AleVT
[T] (Teletext) and Nxtvepg (NextView) and supports the bttv, bktr & dvb APIs.
[T] It contains some deinterlacing filters and record video files with various
[T] containers (AVI, MPEG, OGG, etc.) and many codecs.

